(b) Legitimate interests – running our business; increasing the functionality of the Service and user friendliness; improving the quality of our Service; ensuring that users have the best possible experience when using our Service
To better understand how you use our Service, your behaviour and preferences; develop and enhance the Game and gaming experience; provide chat features as part of the Service; personalise player experience.
(a) Your consent
(b) Legitimate interests – keeping our Service updated and relevant; improving our Service; providing the best possible experience to our users
